
*** ROS package: ros_amy ***

ros_amy (ROS package) allows controlling a robot arm through the amy library.

To use it you need to:

- get amy.git repo
- create a catkin workspace
- build the ROS node


> Download amy repo:

git clone https://github.com/albarral/amy.git


> Create the catkin workspace (from terminal):

cd path_to_amy/ws_amy/src
catkin_init_workspace

(note: path_to_amy = amy installation path)


> Build the ROS node (from terminal):

cd path_to_amy/ws_amy
source devel/setup.bash
catkin_make

(note: path_to_amy = amy installation path)


> Nodes in amy_ros package:

ros_amyarm




